Subject: drm/aspeed: Call drm_fbdev_generic_setup after drm_dev_register
Git-commit: 2249357459c0a52608678c27ebc74c4238204057
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc6
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

